{"id":371250,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":22}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"170","ytitle":"","mtitle":"病中书","ftitle":"","authors":["赵琳"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海西郊真北社　赵琳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的同志:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才几天不见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛过了几个冬夏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身虽躺在病床，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心仍在乡下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想念着:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"试验田的洋山芋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可曾丰收?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大路东的茭白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可曾上市?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队里的文盲可曾扫掉?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那里可办起了农民食堂?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农具改了多少?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坌地还用铁耙?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车水还用脚踏?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唉!一条肠子两下里挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫人急死啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨不得变成一只布谷鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窜出病房窗帘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞回乡下骑上千里马。"}]}